Narrator: I stood with Vina on the back terra...
en


I stood with Vina on the back terrace of my palace in Monqiz.

LineNo: 13031175,

Narrator: Her palace, now.
en


Her palace, now.

LineNo: 13031555,

Narrator: Grey clouds hung low on the horizon...
en


Grey clouds hung low on the horizon. A strong wind was picking up, and waves crashed violently on the rocky cliffs below us.

LineNo: 13031657,

Narrator: I stood on the back terrace of my p...
en


I stood on the back terrace of my palace in Monqiz.

LineNo: 13031759,

Narrator: Grey clouds hung low on the horizon...
en


Grey clouds hung low on the horizon. A strong wind was picking up, and waves crashed violently on the rocky cliffs below me.

LineNo: 13031861,

Vina Toras: So I'm to be a half-sister. I supp...
en


"So I'm to be a half-sister. I suppose congratulations are in order."

LineNo: 13031963,

Narrator: She ran a hand along the terrace's...
en


She ran a hand along the terrace's gold-plated railing.

LineNo: 13032089,

Narrator: The future king of Rizia. At least...
en


The future king of Rizia. At least as the law would have it.

LineNo: 13032191,

Narrator: I'd met Vina here to tell her priva...
en


I'd met Vina here to tell her privately before informing the world. As I looked at her stony expression, I wondered if I had made a mistake.

LineNo: 13032293,

Player_Romus: Why, thank you. I accept.
en


"Why, thank you. I accept."

LineNo: 13032395,

Player_Romus: I know that this is a lot to take...
en


"I know that this is a lot to take in."

LineNo: 13032497,

Player_Romus: Please. At least try to be happy f...
en


"Please. At least try to be happy for me."

LineNo: 13032599,

Player_Romus: You'll always be my favorite, Vina.
en


"You'll always be my favorite, Vina."

LineNo: 13032701,

Vina Toras: Yes. It is.
en


"Yes. It is."

LineNo: 13032803,

Vina Toras: That's all you have to say?
en


"That's all you have to say?"

LineNo: 13032905,

Vina Toras: I am trying.
en


"I am trying."

LineNo: 13033007,

Vina Toras: In what way?
en


"In what way?"

LineNo: 13033109,

Vina Toras: I've based my entire life on the i...
en


"I've based my entire life on the idea that I was the future queen of Rizia."

LineNo: 13033211,

Vina Toras: I spent so many hours attending co...
en


"I spent so many hours attending council meetings..."

LineNo: 13033869,

Vina Toras: I went to so many balls and etique...
en


"I went to so many balls and etiquette classes..."

LineNo: 13033971,

Vina Toras: I gave up the chance to be with th...
en


"I gave up the chance to be with the man I loved..."

LineNo: 13034351,

Vina Toras: I let you talk me into marrying my...
en


"I let you talk me into marrying my own cousin, because you said that was what was expected of the heir to House Toras!"

LineNo: 13034453,

Vina Toras: All while you went about consolida...
en


"All while you went about consolidating your power, even getting rid of the House of Delegates to keep yourself and your... son in charge."

LineNo: 13034833,

Vina Toras: I went to Pales as the heiress to...
en


"I went to Pales as the heiress to the Rizian throne, and we all know what happened there..."

LineNo: 13035491,

Vina Toras: All while you went about making li...
en


"All while you went about making life miserable for the commoners."

LineNo: 13035871,

Vina Toras: All while you went about making re...
en


"All while you went about making reforms that I suggested without even consulting me on them."

LineNo: 13035973,

Narrator: She wrapped her kerchief tighter ar...
en


She wrapped her kerchief tighter around her head as a gust of wind blew.

LineNo: 13036075,

Vina Toras: Tell me, Father. What was it all f...
en


"Tell me, Father. What was it all for?"

LineNo: 13036201,

Player_Romus: Vina. Don't you remember when we w...
en


"Vina. Don't you remember when we were sitting down there on the beach and I warned you that exactly this might happen?"

LineNo: 13036581,

Player_Romus: Nothing is decided yet. You may st...
en


"Nothing is decided yet. You may still get your chance to be queen."

LineNo: 13036953,

Player_Romus: I haven't forgotten what I told yo...
en


"I haven't forgotten what I told you down there on the beach long ago. Rizia's succession laws need not stay in place."

LineNo: 13037055,

Player_Romus: Listen. I would love to name you m...
en


"Listen. I would love to name you my successor. But it's very complicated."

LineNo: 13037427,

Player_Romus: What the hell, Vina? You go on and...
en


"What the hell, Vina? You go on and on about wanting change, and now you're begging to be named successor to a position that doesn't even hold weight anymore?"

LineNo: 13037529,

Narrator: Her eyes brimmed over with fury. Sh...
en


Her eyes brimmed over with fury. She opened her mouth to retaliate, then shut it and sat down heavily on the nearest settee.

LineNo: 13037631,

Vina Toras: You're right. Of course you're rig...
en


"You're right. Of course you're right."

LineNo: 13038011,

Vina Toras: Because it's all I fucking have, F...
en


"Because it's all I fucking have, Father!"

LineNo: 13038113,

Narrator: Her eyes brimmed over with fury. Sh...
en


Her eyes brimmed over with fury. She stalked away and sat down heavily on the nearest settee.

LineNo: 13038215,

Vina Toras: Circumstances have changed, haven'...
en


"Circumstances have changed, haven't they?"

LineNo: 13038595,

Narrator: She blinked.
en


She blinked.

LineNo: 13038697,

Vina Toras: Really?
en


"Really?"

LineNo: 13038823,

Vina Toras: I-- I know.
en


"I-- I know."

LineNo: 13039203,

Vina Toras: You already broke the rules on my...
en


"You already broke the rules on my behalf once. I won't ask you to do it twice."

LineNo: 13039305,

Narrator: She blinked.
en


She blinked.

LineNo: 13039407,

Vina Toras: You mean that?
en


"You mean that?"

LineNo: 13039533,

Player_Romus: Yes. Lucita and I are in love and...
en


"Yes. Lucita and I are in love and having a child together. Whether that child takes the throne doesn't matter to us."

LineNo: 13039635,

Vina Toras: Not for me. I have nothing else le...
en


"Not for me. I have nothing else left."

LineNo: 13040015,

Vina Toras: Yes. I know.
en


"Yes. I know."

LineNo: 13040117,

Narrator: Her eyes brimmed over with fury. Sh...
en


Her eyes brimmed over with fury. She stalked away and sat down heavily on the nearest settee.

LineNo: 13040219,

Narrator: She walked a few steps away and sat...
en


She walked a few steps away and sat down heavily on the nearest settee.

LineNo: 13040321,

Vina Toras: But I will say this.
en


"But I will say this."

LineNo: 13040701,

Vina Toras: My darling husband doesn't give a...
en


"My darling husband doesn't give a damn whether he's Crown Prince Consort or not. But his family does."

LineNo: 13040803,

Vina Toras: My darling husband married me with...
en


"My darling husband married me with the expectation that his children would inherit the throne of Rizia."

LineNo: 13040905,

Vina Toras: If that doesn't happen... well, I...
en


"If that doesn't happen... well, I don't see the big Rizia-Pales reunion lasting for very long."

LineNo: 13041031,

Vina Toras: You favored them greatly by return...
en


"You favored them greatly by returning Zille to Brenas. Name me your heir, and you'll have their loyalty forever."

LineNo: 13041427,

Vina Toras: Whether or not it's symbolic is of...
en


"Whether or not it's symbolic is of no consequence."

LineNo: 13041529,

Player_Romus: You're underestimating the threat...
en


"You're underestimating the threat of the Azaros. If I rob my son of his birthright, it'll be both of our heads on the chopping block."

LineNo: 13041631,

Player_Romus: Tradition is tradition. Your husba...
en


"Tradition is tradition. Your husband and his family will just have to respect that."

LineNo: 13041733,

Vina Toras: Let me just say this.
en


"Let me just say this."

LineNo: 13042113,

Vina Toras: I am the Duchess of Valenqiris. Th...
en


"I am the Duchess of Valenqiris. The only person House Toras loves more than me is Rico."

LineNo: 13042493,

Vina Toras: And I'm married to him.
en


"And I'm married to him."

LineNo: 13042873,

Vina Toras: And you did away with him.
en


"And you did away with him."

LineNo: 13042975,

Vina Toras: If I'm removed as heir to the thro...
en


"If I'm removed as heir to the throne, there'll be hell to pay from my province."

LineNo: 13043379,

Player_Romus: You don't even have any marriage p...
en


"You don't even have any marriage prospects. You're as barren as a fig tree in winter."

LineNo: 13043481,

Vina Toras: And whose fault is that?
en


"And whose fault is that?"

LineNo: 13043583,

Player_Romus: Don't threaten me, young lady.
en


"Don't threaten me, young lady."

LineNo: 13043685,

Vina Toras: It's not a threat. It's the truth.
en


"It's not a threat. It's the truth."

LineNo: 13043787,

Player_Romus: I understand that. I am weighing m...
en


"I understand that. I am weighing my options carefully."

LineNo: 13043889,

Vina Toras: I am the wife of Rico Toras. Our h...
en


"I am the wife of Rico Toras. Our house is expecting our bloodline to keep the throne. No Azaros invited."

LineNo: 13044269,

Vina Toras: If I'm removed as heir to the thro...
en


"If I'm removed as heir to the throne, there'll be hell to pay from Valenqiris."

LineNo: 13044395,

Player_Romus: On the bright side, you'll no long...
en


"On the bright side, you'll no longer be expected to bear children with Ricardus."

LineNo: 13044497,

Vina Toras: If things go on this way, I can't...
en


"If things go on this way, I can't be held responsible for what I'll do."

LineNo: 13044623,

Player_Romus: The Royal Council reshuffle is com...
en


"The Royal Council reshuffle is coming up. What if I gave you a promotion?"

LineNo: 13044725,

Vina Toras: I can't promise that they will.
en


"I can't promise that they will."

LineNo: 13044827,

Vina Toras: It's not his birthright if you cha...
en


"It's not his birthright if you change the law."

LineNo: 13044929,

Vina Toras: That's all I can ask.
en


"That's all I can ask."

LineNo: 13045031,

Vina Toras: Well. That is one saving grace.
en


"Well. That is one saving grace."

LineNo: 13045133,

Narrator: She paused. I saw a spark in her ey...
en


She paused. I saw a spark in her eyes.

LineNo: 13045505,

Vina Toras: But... it matters to House Azaro.
en


"But... it matters to House Azaro."

LineNo: 13045885,

Vina Toras: Even if the throne is only symboli...
en


"Even if the throne is only symbolic at this point."

LineNo: 13046011,

Player_Romus: I'm still weighing my options. It'...
en


"I'm still weighing my options. It's complicated."

LineNo: 13046113,

Player_Romus: I know what a good monarch you'll...
en


"I know what a good monarch you'll be. You deserve it."

LineNo: 13046215,

Narrator: She gave me a grateful half-smile.
en


She gave me a grateful half-smile.

LineNo: 13046317,

Vina Toras: But what about House Azaro? I'm su...
en


"But what about House Azaro? I'm sure they'll be furious if their heir isn't named successor."

LineNo: 13046697,

Player_Romus: Your Aunt Bea would have my nether...
en


"Your Aunt Bea would have my nether parts on a guillotine if I removed Rumburgian blood from the line of succession."

LineNo: 13046799,

Vina Toras: She would, wouldn't she?
en


"She would, wouldn't she?"

LineNo: 13046901,

Player_Romus: I can't take your mother's blood o...
en


"I can't take your mother's blood out of the line of succession. I owe her that much."

LineNo: 13047003,

Vina Toras: If you think I'm qualified enough....
en


"If you think I'm qualified enough..."

LineNo: 13047105,

Narrator: Her head whipped towards the door....
en


Her head whipped towards the door. Lucita had come to fetch me.

LineNo: 13047207,

Player_Romus: Leave me to deal with the Azaros.
en


"Leave me to deal with the Azaros."

LineNo: 13047309,

Player_Romus: That's a good point. This won't be...
en


"That's a good point. This won't be an easy decision to make."

LineNo: 13047411,

Player_Romus: The Azaros aren't the only player...
en


"The Azaros aren't the only player on this chess board. Don't forget about your husband."

LineNo: 13047783,

Vina Toras: If they retaliate, I'll be the one...
en


"If they retaliate, I'll be the one they go after first."

LineNo: 13047917,

Player_Romus: You're thinking in such medieval t...
en


"You're thinking in such medieval terms. All three of Rizia's noble houses should be able to live in peace together."

LineNo: 13048019,

Player_Romus: You're the one that wants to be qu...
en


"You're the one that wants to be queen. Are you willing to spend the rest of your life looking over your shoulder?"

LineNo: 13048121,

Narrator: She set her jaw.
en


She set her jaw.

LineNo: 13048223,

Vina Toras: Yes. I think so.
en


"Yes. I think so."

LineNo: 13048325,

Vina Toras: Ideally, yes. Some of these people...
en


"Ideally, yes. Some of these people seem to have no idea it's 1958."

LineNo: 13048427,

Vina Toras: Yes, of course he and his family a...
en


"Yes, of course he and his family are a factor."

LineNo: 13048529,

Vina Toras: Speaking of which...
en


"Speaking of which..."

LineNo: 13048631,

Vina Toras: You're running out of time to make...
en


"You're running out of time to make it."

LineNo: 13048733,

Narrator: It had been a few months since her...
en


It had been a few months since her doctor's appointment in Porte Drazon, and her belly was beginning to curve outwards. Vina curtsied politely.

LineNo: 13048931,

Vina Toras: Hello, Duchess Azaro. Or rather, Y...
en


"Hello, Duchess Azaro. Or rather, Your Majesty."

LineNo: 13049033,

Lucita Azaro: Please. 'Lucita' will do just fine.
en


"Please. 'Lucita' will do just fine."

LineNo: 13049135,

Lucita Azaro: I take it your father's told you t...
en


"I take it your father's told you the good news?"

LineNo: 13049237,

Lucita Azaro: They'll be ready for the announcem...
en


"They'll be ready for the announcement in five minutes, Romus."

LineNo: 13049355,

Player_Romus: I don't need five minutes. I know...
en


"I don't need five minutes. I know what I'm going to say."

LineNo: 13049457,

Player_Romus: Splendid. I'll be right in.
en


"Splendid. I'll be right in."

LineNo: 13049559,

Player_Romus: Leave me to think. Both of you.
en


"Leave me to think. Both of you."

LineNo: 13049661,

Narrator: My wife and my daugther both smiled...
en


My wife and my daugther both smiled with confidence, then looked at each other suspiciously.

LineNo: 13049763,

Narrator: Lucita took my hand and led me insi...
en


Lucita took my hand and led me inside the palace. Vina followed from a distance.

LineNo: 13049865,

Vina Toras: Yes, Father.
en


"Yes, Father."

LineNo: 13049967,

Lucita Azaro: Of course.
en


"Of course."

LineNo: 13050069,

Narrator: Both my wife and daughter gave me m...
en


Both my wife and daughter gave me meaningful looks before turning around and heading in.

LineNo: 13050171,

Lucita Azaro: Let's go, then.
en


"Let's go, then."

LineNo: 13050273,

Narrator: The normally spacious sitting room...
en


The normally spacious sitting room of Palas Toras had been filled with lighting and camera equipment, all pointed at the purple velvet divan against the back wall.

LineNo: 13050375,

Narrator: Above it hung portraits of Ana Azar...
en


Above it hung portraits of Ana Azaro and Ariana Toras.

LineNo: 13050477,

Narrator: Lucita and I were seated. An assist...
en


Lucita and I were seated. An assistant quickly refreshed our makeup.

LineNo: 13050579,

Narrator: The camerawoman counted down from f...
en


The camerawoman counted down from five. It was time for my royal address.

LineNo: 13050713,

Narrator: I looked once more at the turbulent...
en


I looked once more at the turbulent ocean.

LineNo: 13051093,

Narrator: Was I ready to sever my ties with m...
en


Was I ready to sever my ties with my late wife?

LineNo: 13051195,

Narrator: Even if I hadn't loved Lena... was...
en


Even if I hadn't loved Lena... was I ready to sever all ties with her?

LineNo: 13051297,

Narrator: What would be the cost of breaking...
en


What would be the cost of breaking tradition and naming our daughter as heiress?

LineNo: 13051399,

Vina Toras: The current succession law is sexi...
en


"The current succession law is sexist and outdated. The eldest *child* should inherit the throne, not the eldest son."

LineNo: 13051501,

Vina Toras: But furthermore...
en


"But furthermore..."

LineNo: 13051603,

Vina Toras: If you want to continue the progre...
en


"If you want to continue the progress Queen Lyza started, it's only natural to acknowledge the eldest *child*, not the eldest son, should inherit the throne."

LineNo: 13051705,

Vina Toras: Furthermore...
en


"Furthermore..."

LineNo: 13051807,

Narrator: And would it be worse than the cost...
en


And would it be worse than the cost of keeping it?

LineNo: 13051909,

Narrator: I steeled myself and headed inside.
en


I steeled myself and headed inside.

LineNo: 13052203,

Player_Romus: My fellow Rizians.
en


"My fellow Rizians."

LineNo: 13052305,

Player_Romus: That's right, another speech from...
en


"That's right, another speech from your king. I hope you're not sick of me yet."

LineNo: 13052677,

Player_Romus: My dear subjects.
en


"My dear subjects."

LineNo: 13053049,

Player_Romus: O children of this blessed land.
en


"O children of this blessed land."

LineNo: 13053151,

Player_Romus: My friends and countrypeople.
en


"My friends and countrypeople."

LineNo: 13053253,

Player_Romus: After so many years as a widower,...
en


"After so many years as a widower, I am happy to announce that I have found true love again."

LineNo: 13053689,

Player_Romus: Your King has an announcement to m...
en


"Your King has an announcement to make."

LineNo: 13053815,

Player_Romus: Allow me to present, for the very...
en


"Allow me to present, for the very first time, Queen Consort Lucita Azaro."

LineNo: 13053933,

Player_Romus: I hope you have all grown to love...
en


"I hope you have all grown to love my wife Lucita as you have grown to love me."

LineNo: 13054059,

Player_Romus: You all know Duchess Lucita Azaro...
en


"You all know Duchess Lucita Azaro as the woman who won us the Pales war. Now you shall get to know her as your new queen."

LineNo: 13054177,

Player_Romus: In the wake of our triumph in the...
en


"In the wake of our triumph in the Pales war, we have yet another achievement to announce."

LineNo: 13054581,

Player_Romus: You all know Duchess Lucita Azaro...
en


"You all know Duchess Lucita Azaro as my war and security councilor. But now, you shall get to know her as your new queen."

LineNo: 13055239,

Player_Romus: In the wake of protests that are t...
en


"In the wake of protests that are threatening to tear the nation apart, I have news that may bring you some comfort."

LineNo: 13055365,

Player_Romus: I am pleased to tell you all that...
en


"I am pleased to tell you all that the Queen Consort is about to bear me a son."

LineNo: 13055467,

Narrator: Lucita placed a hand on my shoulder...
en


Lucita placed a hand on my shoulder and smiled for the cameras.

LineNo: 13055593,

Player_Romus: We are having a child. A baby boy.
en


"We are having a child. A baby boy."

LineNo: 13055965,

Player_Romus: Despite my wife's advancing years,...
en


"Despite my wife's advancing years, the Lord has seen fit to sprout the seed of new life in her womb."

LineNo: 13056345,

Player_Romus: We were married by secret ceremony...
en


"We were married by secret ceremony, the legitimacy of which shall not come into question."

LineNo: 13056471,

Player_Romus: I shall never forget Princess Cons...
en


"I shall never forget Princess Consort Lena. But Queen Lucita and I are happy to welcome new love into Palas Rezna."

LineNo: 13056597,

Player_Romus: We were married in an intimate cer...
en


"We were married in an intimate ceremony before the eyes of Grand Wiseman Ignacius."

LineNo: 13056723,

Player_Romus: Forbidden flirtations in the counc...
en


"Forbidden flirtations in the council chamber have transformed into a love that shall resonate throughout history."

LineNo: 13056841,

Player_Romus: There is more good news. We are ha...
en


"There is more good news. We are having a child. A baby boy."

LineNo: 13056943,

Player_Romus: The Royal Family is about to be bl...
en


"The Royal Family is about to be blessed with young blood."

LineNo: 13057045,

Player_Romus: She will shortly be leaving the co...
en


"She will shortly be leaving the council to pursue a new role. That of mother."

LineNo: 13057417,

Player_Romus: Despite my wife's advancing years,...
en


"Despite my wife's advancing years, the Lord has seen fit to plant the seed of new life in her womb."

LineNo: 13057519,

Player_Romus: Furthermore, I am pleased to annou...
en


"Furthermore, I am pleased to announce that your new Queen Consort is already pregnant with a son."

LineNo: 13057621,

Player_Romus: His name shall be Prince Romus the...
en


"His name shall be Prince Romus the Second."

LineNo: 13057723,

Player_Romus: His name shall be Prince Taddeus t...
en


"His name shall be Prince Taddeus the Second."

LineNo: 13057825,

Player_Romus: His name shall be Prince Valero th...
en


"His name shall be Prince Valero the Second."

LineNo: 13058197,

Player_Romus: I shall name him Ardos, after one...
en


"I shall name him Ardos, after one of the most devout Wruhecist disciples."

LineNo: 13058299,

Narrator: I paused for dramatic effect.
en


I paused for dramatic effect.

LineNo: 13058425,

Narrator: Lucita's smile grew taut.
en


Lucita's smile grew taut.

LineNo: 13058527,

Narrator: Lucita's smile grew wider.
en


Lucita's smile grew wider.

LineNo: 13058629,

Player_Romus: According to the traditions of thi...
en


"According to the traditions of this great kingdom, a monarch shall be succeeded by his or her eldest son. A woman can inherit the throne only if she has no brothers."

LineNo: 13059017,

Player_Romus: As you all know, Rizia is now a co...
en


"As you all know, Rizia is now a constitutional monarchy. The line of succession does not carry as much importance as it used to."

LineNo: 13059135,

Player_Romus: My daughter left us before her tim...
en


"My daughter left us before her time. Since then, the question of who will be your ruler after I am gone has been unclear."

LineNo: 13059539,

Player_Romus: With my daughter gone forever, my...
en


"With my daughter gone forever, my son has every right to claim the title of Crown Prince."

LineNo: 13059935,

Player_Romus: I will soon have two children, a s...
en


"I will soon have two children, a son and a daughter. One of them will be your ruler after I am gone."

LineNo: 13060061,

Player_Romus: Though I am overjoyed at becoming...
en


"Though I am overjoyed at becoming a father for the second time, I cannot neglect the inspiration my daughter Vina has been to this country and to me."

LineNo: 13060179,

Player_Romus: I hereby declare an exception to o...
en


"I hereby declare an exception to our kingdom's laws. Princess Vina Toras will remain my successor."

LineNo: 13060281,

Player_Romus: I hereby declare an exception to t...
en


"I hereby declare an exception to the law. Princess Vina Sazon will remain my successor."

LineNo: 13060383,

Player_Romus: I hereby declare an exception to t...
en


"I hereby declare an exception to the law. Princess Vina Reinhart will remain my successor."

LineNo: 13060485,

Player_Romus: I hereby declare that from hencefo...
en


"I hereby declare that from henceforth, Rizian succession law will favor a king's eldest daughter, not his son. It is time to turn the tables."

LineNo: 13060491,

Player_Romus: I hereby declare that from hencefo...
Menu Text en


"I hereby declare that from henceforth, Rizian succession law will favor a king's eldest daughter, not his son. It is time to turn the tables." [-5 Authority]

LineNo: 13060863,

Player_Romus: In accordance with Rizian law. I s...
en


"In accordance with Rizian law. I shall be succeeded by the son of Queen Consort Lucita Toras."

LineNo: 13060965,

Player_Romus: In recognition of the contribution...
en


"In recognition of the contributions made by the honorable House Azaro to this kingdom, I am proud to officially name their new heir as my successor."

LineNo: 13061067,

Narrator: Lucita's grip tightened on my shoul...
en


Lucita's grip tightened on my shoulder. Her nails practically pierced through my suit jacket.

LineNo: 13061281,

Player_Romus: However, choosing an official succ...
en


"However, choosing an official successor was not an easy decision for me."

LineNo: 13061671,

Player_Romus: With that in mind, choosing an off...
